IMAPAccount ira
Host imap.1und1.de
User christopher@ira-kunststoffe.de
PassCmd "pass imap/ira/christopher"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore ira-remote
Account ira

MaildirStore ira-local
Path ~/.mail/ira/
Inbox ~/.mail/ira/Inbox

Channel ira
Master :ira-remote:
Slave :ira-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *

